{"type":null,"faqId":8589,"title":"WS331a无线中继（Repeater）模式的使用场景是什么？如何从路由模式切换到中继模式？","answer":"&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">您是不是正在因为房间里的</span><span>Wi-Fi</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">信号时断时续而异常苦恼？这个时候您就可以使用</span><span>WS331a</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的</span><span>Repeater</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">功能，扩展您家的</span><span>Wi-Fi</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">覆盖范围。当然，使用</span><span>Repeater</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的前提是，您家里已经有一个无线路由器了。</span> \n<p style=\"text-indent:0cm;margin-left:0cm;\">\n\t<span>1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、登录</span><span>Web</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">配置界面。</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:0cm;margin-left:0cm;\">\n\t<span>2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、点击“<b>家庭网络</b></span><b><span> &gt; </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">无线中继设置</span><span> &gt; </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">中继连接设置</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">”。</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:0cm;margin-left:0cm;\">\n\t<span>3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、勾选“<b>开启中继（</b></span><b><span>Repeater</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）功能</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">”。</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:0cm;margin-left:0cm;\">\n\t<span>4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、根据页面提示将</span><span>WS331a</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">连接到您想要扩展的</span><span>Wi-Fi</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:0cm;margin-left:0cm;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=28196\" /></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:0cm;margin-left:0cm;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span>&nbsp;\n</p>","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9077","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null